Former Dutch MP Ayaan Hirsi Ali on her life under armed guard. Also, Chinese environmentalists feeding China's last wild elephants. Father Cadfan of Belmont Abbey, UK visits his first football match with Leeds United fan Gary Edwards. The friendship between a carer and resident at a New York care home which bridges a 73 year age gap. Presenter: Frederick Dove. Show less